quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  3,16,"Allatheena yaqooloona rabbanainnana amanna faghfir lana thunoobanawaqina AAathaba annar"
  3,17,"Assabireena wassadiqeenawalqaniteena walmunfiqeena walmustaghfireenabil-ashar"
  3,18,"Shahida Allahu annahu la ilahailla huwa walmala-ikatu waoloo alAAilmi qa-imanbilqisti la ilaha illa huwaalAAazeezu alhakeem"
  3,19,"Inna addeena AAinda Allahial-islamu wama ikhtalafa allatheena ootooalkitaba illa min baAAdi ma jaahumualAAilmu baghyan baynahum waman yakfur bi-ayati Allahifa-inna Allaha sareeAAu alhisab"
  3,20,"Fa-in hajjooka faqul aslamtu wajhiyalillahi wamani ittabaAAani waqul lillatheena ootooalkitaba walommiyyeena aaslamtum fa-inaslamoo faqadi ihtadaw wa-in tawallaw fa-innama AAalaykaalbalaghu wallahu baseerun bilAAibad"
  3,21,"Inna allatheena yakfuroona bi-ayatiAllahi wayaqtuloona annabiyyeena bighayri haqqinwayaqtuloona allatheena ya/muroona bilqistimina annasi fabashshirhum biAAathabin aleem"
  3,22,"Ola-ika allatheena habitataAAmaluhum fee addunya wal-akhiratiwama lahum min nasireen"
